d not support the disney brands bhatia got the disney catalog distributed by the disney stores which had not happen much before which generated sales of  million at lower mailing costs she then found that disney had multiple  customer databases of which only five were used for catalog mailings combined the  databases had  million records that after removing duplicated records consisted of  million households with the unified database disney started adding additional catalogs started in spring  with the walt disney gallery catalog plus two more by june  with the increased sales a new warehouse was being build in south carolina with disneys purchase of the remainder of infoseek in july  the go network infoseek the disney catalog disney online disneycom and disneystorecom abc news internet ventures and espn internet ventures and buena vista internet group are merged into the gocom company disney shoppingedit disney direct marketing services inc had changed its name to disney shopping inc as it operated online with the disneyshoppingcom domain by january   disney shoppings kansas call center was closed with some of the  employees would transferring to a utah call center and few would remain until may  on may   disneyshoppingcom was redesigned and relaunched at a new domain disneystorecom with the additional of disney parks and resorts products catalogsedit disney catalog walt disney gallery spring  a twice a year collectibles catalog which has also been sent to lenox mint danbury mint and franklin mint catalog lists by june   its circulation was  million copies per year and generating  million in annual sales disney kids by july  send to parents twice a year in august focusing on backtoschool and in september focusing on halloween costumes by june   its circulation was  million copies per year and generating  million in annual sales disneystorecom formerly disneyshoppingcom pooh’s corner  for the fans of the bear character by june   its circulation was  million copies p